These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, lettuce, raspberry, apricot
4 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, fish, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, boat, motorbike, skateboard
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the pony##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the hamster is between the person driving the motorbike and the person eating lettuce##2
6. the person driving the boat is the owner of the fish##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | raspberry | apricot  | lettuce | cucumber  |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | hamster  | pony       | fish     |
| Transport   | motorbike     | bus | skateboard       | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, fishing, puzzles, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, crime, romance, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, biathlon, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing    | cooking  | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | epic  | crime   | romance    |
| Sport         | rugby | snowboarding | weightlifting | biathlon      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, water, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, hiking, card-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, electronic, trance, jazz
1. the fan of electronic is between the fan of jazz and the person drinking coffee##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the fan of trance is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | coffee | milk         | hot-chocolate   | water    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | card-games | chess | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | electronic        | jazz      | r&b   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, canadian, chinese, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, golf, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, airplane, helicopter
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the helicopter and the japanese##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the chinese is on the right of the french##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | japanese        | canadian   | french | chinese |
| Sport         | golf | basketball | rugby    | snowboarding |
| Transport     | airplane       | train     | helicopter       | subway    |

