.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, collecting, fishing, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding, badminton, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk      | mirinda       | sprite   |
| Hobby      | cooking   | collecting  | camping | fishing     |
| Sport      | snowboarding     | rowing | badminton        | skateboarding |

