.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, blueberry, raspberry, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, reading, video-games, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, skiing, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating carrot and the person eating raspberry##2
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | raspberry | blueberry  | carrot | potato      |
| Hobby   | video-games  | sudoku  | woodworking | reading |
| Sport   | rugby | biathlon | tennis | skiing     |

