.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cherry, grapefruit, tomato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, western, musical, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, ice-hockey, biathlon, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person eating cherry is between the person watching western movies and the person watching musical movies##2
7. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit  | cherry    | tomato | broccoli  |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | fantasy       | western        | romance    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | lacrosse | parkour  | biathlon |

