.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, skydiving, dancing, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, sports, mystery, zombie
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, snake, mouse
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person watching sports movies is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | collecting  | skydiving | dancing | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | zombie | sports   | mystery         |
| Pet           | bird | snake  | rat   | mouse      |

