.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, asparagus, radish, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, filmmaking, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, classical, blues, rock
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the fan of blues and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | lemon  | grapefruit    | radish | asparagus       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | collecting | drawing  | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | rock      | classical  | folk     |

