The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, crime, musical, action
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
3. the person eating garlic is between the person eating artichoke and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
7. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person watching family movies is the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
