.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, spinach, carrot
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, drawing, traveling, collecting
4 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, frog, turtle
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person eating corn##1
3. the owner of the pony is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the owner of the pony and the person eating carrot##2
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | carrot  | spinach | cabbage | corn     |
| Hobby   | photography | traveling   | collecting  | drawing    |
| Pet     | lizard        | turtle       | pony      | frog |

