3. the person drinking water is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | sprite     | water | fanta       |
| Hobby      | singing  | collecting | writing  | drawing |
| Pet        | rabbit  | guinea-pig      | hedgehog        | mouse      |

