3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the chef##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching spy movies and the bartender##2
6. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the taxi is the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
