.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, milk, juice
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, jazz, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch, nigerian, indonesian
1. the fan of blues is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking milk and the dutch##2
3. the person drinking milk is the fan of metal##1
4. the person drinking milk is between the fan of jazz and the indonesian##2
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
6. the pakistani is between the nigerian and the fan of salsa##2
7. the fan of blues is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea | milk | almond-milk   | juice |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | metal    | jazz   | salsa     |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | nigerian | pakistani | dutch   |

