.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, almond-milk, fanta
There 4 different types of food: peas, blueberry, strawberry, garlic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, badminton, tennis
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
2. the person eating strawberry is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's sport is badminton##2
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up    | juice | fanta           | almond-milk |
| Food       | peas | strawberry    | blueberry          | garlic   |
| Sport      | badminton  | surfing   | tennis | baseball  |

