.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, coffee, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, musical, western, thriller
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, goat, lizard
1. the person watching western movies is the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person watching western movies and the person watching horror movies##2
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the owner of the lizard is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the pony##2
7. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | coffee | lemonade | fanta     | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | thriller        | western  | musical  |
| Pet           | pony      | lizard         | dog | goat |

