4. the person driving the jet-ski is the security-guard##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person driving the jet-ski##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | doctor        | security-guard  | designer | engineer   |
| Sport       | cycling | lacrosse | soccer    | skateboarding |
| Transport   | boat        | jet-ski     | bike       | bus      |

