.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, radish, pumpkin, lemon
4 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, dog, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, van, tram
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the tram is the owner of the lizard##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person eating lemon and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | lemon | radish | carrot | pumpkin |
| Pet         | frog       | chinchilla     | dog   | lizard   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bus | van | tram |

 